# Frontend — Cursor Agent Rules

## Stack
- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite 5
- React Router v6 (createBrowserRouter, loader pattern)
- TanStack Query v5 (useQuery, useMutation, queryClient)
- Zustand for global state (auth store, cart store)
- Tailwind CSS v3 + shadcn/ui components
- Axios with interceptors (src/lib/axios.ts)
- @react-oauth/google for Google OAuth

## Backend contract
- Spring Boot 4.0.3 running on http://localhost:8080 in dev
- Vite proxies /api/* → http://localhost:8080 (no CORS in dev)
- Auth: Spring Security with JWT stored in httpOnly cookie
- OAuth2: Google login via /oauth2/authorization/google (Spring handles redirect)
- All API base path: /api (e.g. GET /api/products/{id})

